== The NIH Deep Phenotyping Study (Walitt et al.\ 2024)
<sec:nih-deep-phenotyping>

The 2024 NIH Intramural Study, published in _Nature Communications_, represents the most comprehensive and expensive deep phenotyping study of post-infectious ME/CFS to date @walitt2024deep. This landmark study merits detailed examination both for its substantial biological contributions and for the significant methodological controversies it generated.

